1
00:00:02,033 --> 00:00:04,966
[ HIDENORI TOKUYAMA'S
"STILL TIME" PLAYS ]

2
00:00:09,233 --> 00:00:11,933
[ MAN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

3
00:01:34,183 --> 00:01:36,283
-SO, LET'S BEGIN.

4
00:01:40,283 --> 00:01:43,550
-[ GRUNTING ]

5
00:01:47,398 --> 00:01:49,498
-THAT'S RIGHT, GOKU.
LET GO.

6
00:01:49,598 --> 00:01:53,432
LET GO OF ALL YOUR RAGE,
ALL YOUR HUNGER.

7
00:01:53,532 --> 00:01:57,365
LET YOURSELF BECOME THE SPARK
THAT IGNITES THE FORMATION

8
00:01:57,465 --> 00:01:59,398
OF THE NEW HEAVEN AND EARTH.

9
00:01:59,498 --> 00:02:01,732
YOU ARE THE CREATOR.

10
00:02:01,832 --> 00:02:04,265
-[ SCREAMING ]

11
00:02:04,365 --> 00:02:06,398
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLING ]

12
00:02:12,232 --> 00:02:14,198
[ SCREAMING CONTINUES ]

13
00:02:20,132 --> 00:02:22,965
-THAT'S GOOD, GOKU.

14
00:02:23,065 --> 00:02:25,265
LET IT ALL OUT.

15
00:02:25,365 --> 00:02:26,332
OHH!

16
00:02:26,432 --> 00:02:28,098
[ GRUNTING ]

17
00:02:31,265 --> 00:02:33,265
NOT YET.

18
00:02:34,765 --> 00:02:38,265
I'M NOT --
NOT READY TO LET --

19
00:02:38,365 --> 00:02:41,032
LET THIS LIFE END YET.

20
00:02:41,132 --> 00:02:42,432
-STEP ASIDE.

21
00:02:42,532 --> 00:02:44,098
-WHAT'S THE IDEA?

22
00:02:44,198 --> 00:02:46,332
-THIS GUY, HE'S ALL MINE.

23
00:02:46,432 --> 00:02:48,998
-NO NEED TO FIGHT OVER ME,
FELLAS.

24
00:02:49,098 --> 00:02:50,698
I'LL TAKE YOU BOTH ON.

25
00:02:50,798 --> 00:02:52,298
-I DON'T SHARE MY PREY.

26
00:02:52,398 --> 00:02:54,332
-WE'LL SEE WHO'S THE HUNTER.

27
00:02:54,432 --> 00:02:55,632
-PREPARE YOURSELF.

28
00:02:55,732 --> 00:02:57,632
-HYAH!

29
00:03:01,865 --> 00:03:03,365
-WILL YOU STOP THIS?

30
00:03:03,465 --> 00:03:07,532
I HAVE NO WISH TO FIGHT
A WEAK LITTLE CHILD LIKE YOU.

31
00:03:07,632 --> 00:03:08,765
RUN ALONG NOW.

32
00:03:08,865 --> 00:03:10,332
-A CHILD, HUH?

33
00:03:12,265 --> 00:03:14,298
DON'T YOU UNDERESTIMATE ME!

34
00:03:14,398 --> 00:03:16,565
I CAN BE TOUGH WHEN I WANT TO.

35
00:03:16,665 --> 00:03:20,298
-THAT'S TRUE.

36
00:03:22,065 --> 00:03:25,765
THEN I SHALL FIGHT YOU
IN EARNEST.

37
00:03:29,098 --> 00:03:31,698
-[ GRUNTING ]

38
00:03:34,898 --> 00:03:36,565
[ MACHINE-GUN FIRE ]

39
00:03:36,665 --> 00:03:39,832
-DON'T THINK I WON'T FIRE BACK!

40
00:03:39,965 --> 00:03:40,998
AAH!

41
00:03:42,798 --> 00:03:45,365
-CUTE TRICK.

42
00:03:47,098 --> 00:03:50,265
WELL, WE DON'T APPEAR TO BE
GETTING ANYWHERE.

43
00:03:53,032 --> 00:03:55,798
WHAT DO YOU SAY
WE END THIS RIGHT NOW?

44
00:03:55,898 --> 00:03:56,832
-[ CHUCKLES ]

45
00:03:56,932 --> 00:03:58,765
AH, SURE.
WHAT THE HELL?

46
00:03:58,865 --> 00:04:00,765
GO AHEAD AND SHOOT.

47
00:04:00,865 --> 00:04:02,098
WHAT'S WRONG, SANZO?

48
00:04:02,198 --> 00:04:04,698
YOU DIDN'T THINK
I'D PROTECT YOU, DID YOU?

49
00:04:04,798 --> 00:04:06,032
-LIKE HELL.

50
00:04:09,832 --> 00:04:12,065
[ MACHINE-GUN FIRE ]

51
00:04:12,165 --> 00:04:13,732
-[ SQUEALS ]

52
00:04:13,832 --> 00:04:16,532
-[ GRUNTING ]

53
00:04:16,632 --> 00:04:17,732
-HOLD YOUR FIRE.

54
00:04:17,832 --> 00:04:20,198
-I WAS WONDERING
WHERE YOU'D BEEN.

55
00:04:20,298 --> 00:04:22,598
-DAMN.
JUST WHAT I NEED.

56
00:04:22,698 --> 00:04:27,632
-SANZO, WHERE'S GOKU?
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM?

57
00:04:29,365 --> 00:04:32,698
-DON'T TELL ME YOU --
YOU DIDN'T!

58
00:04:32,798 --> 00:04:33,732
-SHUT UP!

59
00:04:33,832 --> 00:04:35,498
-WILL YOU CONTINUE TO BE

60
00:04:35,598 --> 00:04:38,898
THE LITTLE TYKE'S SHINING SON,
SANZO?

61
00:04:40,532 --> 00:04:42,198
-WHAT IS IT?

62
00:04:44,732 --> 00:04:48,465
-WE'RE OUT OF TIME!
DON'T JUST STAND THERE!

63
00:04:48,565 --> 00:04:50,532
LET'S GO FIND GOKU!

64
00:04:55,432 --> 00:04:56,298
-GOJYO.

65
00:04:56,398 --> 00:04:57,232
-WHAT?

66
00:04:57,332 --> 00:04:59,498
-YOU TAKE CARE OF THIS.

67
00:04:59,598 --> 00:05:00,965
-COME AGAIN?

68
00:05:01,065 --> 00:05:03,298
-I'VE GOT THINGS TO DO.

69
00:05:03,398 --> 00:05:05,298
-SANZO.

70
00:05:05,398 --> 00:05:07,465
SANZO!

71
00:05:09,398 --> 00:05:11,565
-"HEAVEN'S DOOR."

72
00:05:17,365 --> 00:05:19,832
[ ELECTRICITY CRACKLES ]

73
00:05:27,265 --> 00:05:29,332
-JUST LOOK AT IT.

74
00:05:29,432 --> 00:05:31,232
IT'S WHAT WE ALWAYS WANTED --

75
00:05:31,332 --> 00:05:36,065
A PLACE WHERE
WE CAN TRULY BE FREE.

76
00:05:42,298 --> 00:05:46,098
OUT HERE,
THERE IS NO HERESY OR TABOOS.

77
00:05:46,198 --> 00:05:50,465
AND A LOVE AS PURE AS OURS
WOULD NEVER BE FORBIDDEN.

78
00:05:58,865 --> 00:06:04,198
-YOU JUST CONTINUE BEING STRONG,
PRIEST GENJO SANZO.

79
00:06:07,332 --> 00:06:09,765
[ FOOTSTEPS ECHOING ]

80
00:06:09,865 --> 00:06:11,965
-WHY ARE YOU FOLLOWING ME?

81
00:06:12,065 --> 00:06:15,532
-THAT JACKASS
TOOK THE SEITEN SCRIPTURE

82
00:06:15,632 --> 00:06:17,965
RIGHT OUT FROM UNDER MY NOSE.

83
00:06:18,065 --> 00:06:21,498
I EXPECT TO GET IT BACK,
WITH INTEREST.

84
00:06:21,598 --> 00:06:25,032
-THAT SCRIPTURE
BELONGS TO MY MASTER.

85
00:06:25,132 --> 00:06:26,898
-MAYBE SO, BUT...

86
00:06:28,765 --> 00:06:33,132
THIS HAS BECOME
A MATTER OF PRIDE.

87
00:06:33,232 --> 00:06:35,565
-IT'S SO FITTING,
ISN'T IT, GOKU,

88
00:06:35,665 --> 00:06:37,465
THAT THE OUTCASTS OF THIS WORLD

89
00:06:37,565 --> 00:06:40,698
SHOULD BE THE FATHERS
OF THE NEXT?

90
00:06:40,798 --> 00:06:43,532
BUT ISN'T THAT HOW IT SHOULD BE?

91
00:06:45,832 --> 00:06:47,298
-WOW.

92
00:06:47,398 --> 00:06:49,565
IT'S SO SHINY.

93
00:06:55,998 --> 00:07:00,332
IT'S LIKE THE SUN.

94
00:07:27,932 --> 00:07:29,065
[ GROWLS ]

95
00:07:29,165 --> 00:07:30,698
-[ GASPS ]

96
00:07:32,965 --> 00:07:34,232
[ GRUNTS ]

97
00:07:34,365 --> 00:07:37,465
[ SCREAMS ]

98
00:07:40,765 --> 00:07:44,932
SO, THIS IS YOUR TRUE NATURE.

99
00:07:51,065 --> 00:07:52,865
-WHOA. WHAT IS IT?

100
00:08:02,398 --> 00:08:03,465
-GET READY.

101
00:08:03,565 --> 00:08:04,265
-WHAT?

102
00:08:04,365 --> 00:08:06,632
-AAH!

103
00:08:11,632 --> 00:08:13,032
-AAAAH!

104
00:08:13,132 --> 00:08:14,698
[ GRUNTS ]

105
00:08:26,798 --> 00:08:29,865
-YOU'VE BEEN A VERY BAD MONKEY.

106
00:08:31,665 --> 00:08:33,632
-[ SHOUTS ]

107
00:08:46,798 --> 00:08:48,698
-NOW YOU'VE DONE IT.

108
00:08:52,965 --> 00:08:55,132
AGAIN.

109
00:08:55,232 --> 00:08:58,098
HE'S SMILING AGAIN.

110
00:08:58,198 --> 00:09:00,198
-STEP ASIDE.

111
00:09:00,298 --> 00:09:02,565
-SANZO, WHAT ARE YOU --

112
00:09:02,665 --> 00:09:06,898
-MONKEYS NEED TO BE TRAINED.

113
00:09:06,998 --> 00:09:09,398
[ GUN CLATTERS ]

114
00:09:10,965 --> 00:09:13,032
-DIDN'T I TELL YOU...

115
00:09:13,132 --> 00:09:16,065
THAT I'D GET MY PRIDE BACK?

116
00:09:21,165 --> 00:09:24,798
IT'S BEEN A WHILE
SINCE WE FOUGHT, EH, GOKU?

117
00:09:24,898 --> 00:09:27,265
I GUESS YOU DON'T REMEMBER THAT.

118
00:09:27,365 --> 00:09:31,098
WELL, THEN, SHALL WE START?

119
00:09:31,198 --> 00:09:36,965
-A CREATURE LIKE YOU
IS NOT MEANT TO BE CHAINED.

120
00:09:37,065 --> 00:09:39,532
YOU ARE TRULY ONE OF A KIND.

121
00:09:39,632 --> 00:09:42,698
A SOUL LIKE YOURS
SHOULD BE FREE.

122
00:09:42,798 --> 00:09:45,665
-[ GROWLS ]

123
00:09:47,432 --> 00:09:52,498
-[ SHOUTING ]

124
00:10:04,323 --> 00:10:06,890
-[ GRUNTING ]

125
00:10:08,723 --> 00:10:09,345
[ MACHINE-GUN FIRE ]

126
00:10:09,345 --> 00:10:10,985
-SCURRYING AROUND LIKE RATS.

127
00:10:10,985 --> 00:10:12,652
-YOU'RE LOOKING A LITTLE WINDED.

128
00:10:12,752 --> 00:10:15,552
YOU SHOULD REALLY CUT BACK
ON THOSE CIGARETTES.

129
00:10:15,652 --> 00:10:17,205
-YOU'RE ONE TO TALK.

130
00:10:17,205 --> 00:10:18,438
-EXCELLENT STRATEGY.

131
00:10:18,538 --> 00:10:21,038
I COMMEND YOU
ON YOUR TEAMWORK THUS FAR.

132
00:10:21,138 --> 00:10:23,138
-STOP THIS.

133
00:10:26,871 --> 00:10:31,138
PLEASE, SHIEN, YOU MUST SEE
THAT THIS IS POINTLESS.

134
00:10:31,238 --> 00:10:33,271
-POINTLESS?

135
00:10:33,371 --> 00:10:34,371
-THAT'S RIGHT.

136
00:10:34,471 --> 00:10:36,238
ALL WE WANT IS GOKU RETURNED

137
00:10:36,338 --> 00:10:38,905
AND TO GET BACK
THE MATEN SCRIPTURE.

138
00:10:39,005 --> 00:10:42,738
JUST HAND THEM OVER AND WE
CAN ALL STOP THIS FIGHTING.

139
00:10:42,838 --> 00:10:43,805
IT'S SENSELESS.

140
00:10:43,905 --> 00:10:46,471
-YOU SAID IT, DUDE!
BACK DOWN!

141
00:10:48,338 --> 00:10:49,905
-I CAN'T DO THAT.

142
00:10:50,005 --> 00:10:51,438
-WHY NOT?

143
00:10:51,538 --> 00:10:54,638
-FIGHTING IS ALL WE KNOW.

144
00:10:54,738 --> 00:10:58,271
FIGHTING IS OUR ONLY PURPOSE.

145
00:10:58,371 --> 00:11:03,038
IT IS ONLY IN BATTLE
THAT WE KNOW WE ARE ALIVE.

146
00:11:05,805 --> 00:11:08,871
ZENON AND I HAVE VOWED
TO SERVE HOMURA,

147
00:11:08,971 --> 00:11:12,138
AND WE SHALL DO
WHATEVER HE ASKS OF US.

148
00:11:12,238 --> 00:11:13,171
-[ GASPS ]

149
00:11:13,271 --> 00:11:15,071
THAT MAKES NO SENSE.

150
00:11:15,171 --> 00:11:16,338
-IT'S OKAY.

151
00:11:16,438 --> 00:11:18,271
ONE THING I'VE LEARNED

152
00:11:18,371 --> 00:11:22,771
IS YES-MEN NEVER LEARN
TO SAY NO TO ANYTHING.

153
00:11:24,605 --> 00:11:27,971
-SO, SHALL WE DANCE?

154
00:11:29,738 --> 00:11:31,738
-[ GASPS ]
SHIEN.

155
00:11:33,538 --> 00:11:34,605
-UH?

156
00:11:42,305 --> 00:11:43,105
-SHIEN...

157
00:11:43,205 --> 00:11:45,471
-HOMURA, PLEASE GO ON AHEAD.

158
00:11:45,571 --> 00:11:47,971
I WILL CATCH UP WITH YOU LATER.

159
00:11:48,071 --> 00:11:51,905
I SHOULDN'T THINK THIS WILL TAKE
MORE THAN A FEW MOMENTS,

160
00:11:52,005 --> 00:11:53,871
BUT PLEASE DON'T WAIT UP FOR ME.

161
00:11:53,971 --> 00:11:55,971
I MAY WISH TO PROLONG
THE MOMENT.

162
00:11:56,071 --> 00:11:58,871
-OF COURSE.
PLEASE TAKE YOUR TIME.

163
00:11:58,971 --> 00:12:04,471
-HOW MANY CENTURIES HAS IT BEEN
SINCE I LET MY HAIR DOWN

164
00:12:04,605 --> 00:12:07,338
AND TRULY FOUGHT IN EARNEST?

165
00:12:07,438 --> 00:12:10,771
AND NOW I WILL TEACH YOU...

166
00:12:13,438 --> 00:12:15,405
THE POWER OF GOD.

167
00:12:15,505 --> 00:12:16,805
-[ GASPS ]

168
00:12:17,871 --> 00:12:20,271
-GOD?
DON'T YOU KNOW?

169
00:12:20,371 --> 00:12:22,538
GOD IS DEAD!

170
00:12:25,338 --> 00:12:28,471
-[ SHOUTS ]

171
00:12:28,571 --> 00:12:30,671
-[ GRUNTING ]

172
00:12:33,805 --> 00:12:36,438
-[ GROWLS ]

173
00:12:44,138 --> 00:12:47,805
-HE'S EVEN EVEN STRONGER
THAN BEFORE.

174
00:12:51,438 --> 00:12:53,105
-AAH!

175
00:12:53,205 --> 00:12:55,305
-HUH?

176
00:12:59,105 --> 00:13:00,705
[ CHUCKLES ]

177
00:13:00,805 --> 00:13:01,871
-AW, SHOOT.

178
00:13:01,971 --> 00:13:04,905
-[ SHOUTING ]

179
00:13:10,705 --> 00:13:12,305
-AAH!

180
00:13:15,905 --> 00:13:17,571
-ARE YOU OKAY, YOU GUYS?

181
00:13:17,671 --> 00:13:21,571
-WELL, THEN, IF I HAD KNOWN
YOU WERE THIS GOOD,

182
00:13:21,671 --> 00:13:23,505
I WOULD'VE SAVED MY CHI.

183
00:13:23,605 --> 00:13:24,905
-SO, YOU HAVE REGRETS.

184
00:13:25,005 --> 00:13:26,238
-NO, THAT'S NOT IT.

185
00:13:26,338 --> 00:13:28,805
BELIEVE ME,
I DON'T REGRET A SINGLE THING.

186
00:13:28,905 --> 00:13:32,271
REGRETS ARE JUST A WAY
FOR THE FOOLISH AND THE GUILTY

187
00:13:32,371 --> 00:13:33,338
TO PASS THE TIME.

188
00:13:33,438 --> 00:13:34,505
-IS THAT SO?

189
00:13:34,605 --> 00:13:36,205
-IT IS.
AND I AM.

190
00:13:36,305 --> 00:13:39,505
I'M A FOOL --
A FOOL FOR ALWAYS DWELLING

191
00:13:39,605 --> 00:13:43,471
ON A GUILT-RIDDEN PAST
THAT CAN NEVER BE CHANGED.

192
00:13:43,571 --> 00:13:46,471
I WAS WEAK,
AND I CAN SEE THAT NOW.

193
00:13:46,571 --> 00:13:49,671
-I WOULD HARDLY CALL YOU WEAK,
MY FRIEND.

194
00:13:49,771 --> 00:13:51,405
-THAT'S VERY KIND OF YOU.

195
00:13:51,505 --> 00:13:55,571
BUT TO BE ENTIRELY HONEST,
IF I HAVE ANY STRENGTH AT ALL,

196
00:13:55,671 --> 00:13:58,771
IT'S ONLY BECAUSE
I HAVE A GROUP OF FRIENDS

197
00:13:58,871 --> 00:14:00,471
THAT I NEED TO PROTECT.

198
00:14:00,571 --> 00:14:03,071
-INTERESTING.

199
00:14:03,171 --> 00:14:05,671
IT'S TOO BAD.

200
00:14:05,771 --> 00:14:11,671
I WISH I HAD MORE TIME
TO DISCUSS THIS WITH YOU.

201
00:14:17,771 --> 00:14:20,105
[ SCREAMS ]

202
00:14:22,405 --> 00:14:24,205
[ RUMBLING ]

203
00:14:24,305 --> 00:14:27,571
-I FEAR YOUR FRIENDS
WILL DIE SOON.

204
00:14:27,671 --> 00:14:30,371
-DON'T WORRY.
THEY'RE NOT MY FRIENDS.

205
00:14:30,471 --> 00:14:33,605
THOSE GUYS ARE ONLY MY SERVANTS.
THAT'S ALL.

206
00:14:33,705 --> 00:14:35,805
-[ CHUCKLES ]

207
00:14:41,605 --> 00:14:43,405
-[ GRUNTING ]

208
00:14:43,505 --> 00:14:47,705
I-I'M NOT SURE HOW MUCH LONGER
I CAN HOLD HIM BACK.

209
00:14:47,805 --> 00:14:49,471
DO SOMETHING, GOJYO!

210
00:14:49,571 --> 00:14:52,471
-SO WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO
ABOUT IT?

211
00:14:52,571 --> 00:14:54,871
THIS DUDE'S HARD-CORE, MAN.

212
00:14:54,971 --> 00:14:55,938
-GUYS, HELP ME!

213
00:14:56,038 --> 00:14:58,305
THINK OF SOMETHING QUICK,
WILL YOU?!

214
00:14:58,405 --> 00:15:01,338
-[ SCREECHES ]

215
00:15:01,438 --> 00:15:04,971
-HAKURYUU.

216
00:15:10,771 --> 00:15:11,538
-NO!

217
00:15:11,638 --> 00:15:13,738
-THIS IS POINTLESS.

218
00:15:13,838 --> 00:15:17,205
LAY OFF AND LET ME
HAVE A GO AT THEM.

219
00:15:17,305 --> 00:15:18,705
-NO.

220
00:15:18,805 --> 00:15:22,971
<i>-I THINK I KNOW A WAY</i>
<i>TO SHATTER THIS QIGONG WAVE.</i>

221
00:15:23,071 --> 00:15:25,471
HAKURYUU, YOU TAKE IT FROM HERE!

222
00:15:25,571 --> 00:15:26,671
-[ SQUEALS ]

223
00:15:26,771 --> 00:15:31,205
-[ GRUNTING ]

224
00:15:31,305 --> 00:15:32,538
AAH!

225
00:15:34,305 --> 00:15:38,438
-AH, AN ADMIRABLE EFFORT
BUT INADEQUATE, I'M AFRAID.

226
00:15:38,538 --> 00:15:39,638
-OH?

227
00:15:39,738 --> 00:15:41,938
THEN WHY DO YOU LOOK
SO CONCERNED?

228
00:15:42,038 --> 00:15:46,271
IF I DIDN'T KNOW ANY BETTER,
I'D SAY YOU WERE BITTER.

229
00:15:46,371 --> 00:15:47,605
THAT'S ABSURD.

230
00:15:47,705 --> 00:15:48,438
-IS IT?

231
00:15:48,538 --> 00:15:49,871
CORRECT ME IF I'M WRONG,

232
00:15:49,971 --> 00:15:53,171
BUT I'D SAY YOUR POWER
COMES AT A VERY HEAVY PRICE.

233
00:15:53,271 --> 00:15:56,271
-NOTHING COMES
WITHOUT SACRIFICE, I'M AFRAID.

234
00:15:56,371 --> 00:15:58,371
-BUT TO FORFEIT YOUR FEELINGS?

235
00:15:58,471 --> 00:16:01,038
YOU CLOSED YOURSELF OFF
FOR SO LONG

236
00:16:01,138 --> 00:16:04,338
THAT YOU CAN NO LONGER KNOW
JOY OR PAIN.

237
00:16:04,438 --> 00:16:05,771
-THAT'S NOT TRUE.

238
00:16:05,871 --> 00:16:08,138
-BUT WHAT'S IT ALL FOR?

239
00:16:08,238 --> 00:16:10,971
IS IT JUST TO SERVE HOMURA?

240
00:16:11,071 --> 00:16:13,205
I THINK
IT'S MUCH MORE THAN THAT.

241
00:16:13,305 --> 00:16:15,771
YOU'RE RUNNING AWAY
FROM SOMETHING --

242
00:16:15,871 --> 00:16:17,638
SOMETHING YOU'RE AFRAID OF.

243
00:16:17,738 --> 00:16:18,705
BUT WHAT?

244
00:16:20,571 --> 00:16:22,971
-SHUT UP.

245
00:16:23,071 --> 00:16:25,605
-WHAT ARE YOU RUNNING AWAY FROM?

246
00:16:25,705 --> 00:16:28,771
IS IT SOMETHING
THAT YOU'VE DONE?

247
00:16:28,871 --> 00:16:30,471
-SHUT UP!

248
00:16:30,571 --> 00:16:33,671
-OR PERHAPS IT'S SOMETHING
YOU DIDN'T DO.

249
00:16:33,771 --> 00:16:35,971
IS THAT IT?

250
00:16:36,071 --> 00:16:37,871
-SHUT UP, SHUT UP,
SHUT UP, SHUT UP!

251
00:16:37,971 --> 00:16:40,838
-NOW WHO'S THE ONE WITH REGRETS?

252
00:16:40,938 --> 00:16:41,971
-[ GASPS ]

253
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:47,938
AAH!

254
00:16:48,038 --> 00:16:49,671
-SHIEN!

255
00:16:53,938 --> 00:16:58,005
-[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

256
00:16:58,105 --> 00:17:00,771
-[ GROANING ]

257
00:17:00,871 --> 00:17:02,771
YOU THINK...

258
00:17:02,871 --> 00:17:05,738
THAT I AM A...COWARD?

259
00:17:05,838 --> 00:17:07,105
-I'M SORRY.

260
00:17:07,205 --> 00:17:11,738
I HAD NO RIGHT
TO PRY INTO YOUR PAST LIKE THAT.

261
00:17:11,838 --> 00:17:15,871
I TOOK ADVANTAGE
OF YOUR WEAKNESS.

262
00:17:15,971 --> 00:17:17,105
-I SEE,

263
00:17:17,205 --> 00:17:21,705
AND I SHOULD'VE SEEN
YOUR ATTACK COMING.

264
00:17:21,805 --> 00:17:25,138
I WOULD'VE DONE THE SAME THING.

265
00:17:25,238 --> 00:17:30,138
YOU ARE RIGHT, MY FRIEND,
AND I AM A FOOL...

266
00:17:30,238 --> 00:17:35,671
A FOOL WHO LIVES IN A PAST
THAT CAN'T BE CHANGED.

267
00:17:35,771 --> 00:17:37,138
-SHIEN, NO!

268
00:17:37,238 --> 00:17:41,471
-IT LOOKS LIKE I'M GOING
TO HAVE TO BREAK MY PROMISE.

269
00:17:41,571 --> 00:17:44,138
-NO!
DON'T DO THIS, SHIEN!

270
00:17:44,238 --> 00:17:47,838
-I'M AFRAID IT'S TIME
FOR ME TO MOVE ON.

271
00:17:47,938 --> 00:17:50,438
-THEN MOVE ON TO THE NEW WORLD.

272
00:17:50,538 --> 00:17:52,605
-I'M SORRY.

273
00:17:52,705 --> 00:17:54,471
I MUST GO.

274
00:17:54,571 --> 00:17:56,571
FOR WHAT IT'S WORTH,

275
00:17:56,671 --> 00:18:01,671
IT WAS SUCH A BEAUTIFUL DREAM
WHILE IT LASTED.

276
00:18:04,205 --> 00:18:06,405
AND, HAKKAI,

277
00:18:06,505 --> 00:18:09,838
IT WAS AN HONOR
TO LOSE IN BATTLE

278
00:18:09,938 --> 00:18:12,738
TO SUCH A WORTHY ADVERSARY.

279
00:18:23,604 --> 00:18:25,504
[ RUMBLING ]

280
00:18:44,937 --> 00:18:47,270
-[ SQUEALS ]

281
00:18:48,492 --> 00:18:50,092
-HAKKAI!

282
00:18:50,192 --> 00:18:54,159
-YOU JUST HAD TO PUSH IT.

283
00:18:57,159 --> 00:18:58,392
-I'VE HAD ENOUGH OF THIS.

284
00:18:58,492 --> 00:18:59,826
-HMM?
-HMM?

285
00:19:02,592 --> 00:19:08,092
-IT'S GONNA TAKE MORE THAN
A FEW MIND GAMES TO DEFEAT ME.

286
00:19:08,192 --> 00:19:09,359
-ZENON.

287
00:19:09,459 --> 00:19:12,092
-RELAX, MAN.

288
00:19:14,426 --> 00:19:16,292
[ GROANING ]

289
00:19:25,459 --> 00:19:29,526
-[ GROANING CONTINUES ]

290
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:36,492
-NOW YOU DIE.

291
00:19:47,292 --> 00:19:50,592
-HEY, HOLD ON.

292
00:19:50,692 --> 00:19:54,026
JUST WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

293
00:19:54,126 --> 00:19:55,826
DON'T YOU WANT TO SEE

294
00:19:55,959 --> 00:19:59,692
HOW THIS LITTLE FARCE
OF YOURS PLAYS OUT?

295
00:19:59,792 --> 00:20:03,159
-YOU CAN FILL ME IN LATER.

296
00:20:03,259 --> 00:20:05,159
-YEAH, THAT'S REAL FUNNY.

297
00:20:05,259 --> 00:20:07,792
WAIT TILL I GET AHOLD OF YOU.

298
00:20:13,126 --> 00:20:15,326
HEY, MONKEY.

299
00:20:15,426 --> 00:20:18,026
PLAYTIME'S OVER.

300
00:20:18,126 --> 00:20:23,459
SO IF YOU'RE THROUGH WITH HIM,
LET'S GET STARTED.

301
00:20:27,792 --> 00:20:32,726
-SORRY, GUYS, BUT I...

302
00:20:32,826 --> 00:20:36,892
HAVE TO DO THIS.

303
00:20:46,626 --> 00:20:49,459
[ MIKUNI SHIMOKAWA'S
"ALONE" PLAYS ]

304
00:20:53,726 --> 00:20:56,092
[ WOMAN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

